    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i dont really want to deal with my doctor about this, it's such a hassle. i read on a forum that as long as you taper off the sertraline really fast, you can just start the st john's wort right away to avoid the withdrawal. if i do a quick taper over like 2 or 3 days, would that be safe enough to avoid any bad interactions?",
